{"chapter_number":68,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":2,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"القلم","name_complex":"Al-Qalam","name_simple":"Al-Qalam","verses_count":52,"pages":[564,566],"meaning":{"text":"The Pen","en":"The Pen","id":"Pena"},"verses":[[[1,5272,"68:1","ن ۚ وَالْقَلَمِ وَمَا يَسْطُرُونَ",["Noon. I swear by the pen and what the angels write,","Nun. Demi pena dan apa yang mereka tuliskan,"],564,29,57,226,null,null],[2,5273,"68:2","مَا أَنتَ بِنِعْمَةِ رَبِّكَ بِمَجْنُونٍ",["By the grace of your Lord you are not mad.","dengan karunia Tuhanmu engkau (Muhammad) bukanlah orang gila."],564,29,57,226,null,null],[3,5274,"68:3","وَإِنَّ لَكَ لَأَجْرًا غَيْرَ مَمْنُونٍ",["And most surely you shall have a reward never to be cut off.","Dan sesungguhnya engkau pasti mendapat pahala yang besar yang tidak putus-putusnya."],564,29,57,226,null,null],[4,5275,"68:4","وَإِنَّكَ لَعَلَىٰ خُلُقٍ عَظِيمٍ",["And most surely you conform (yourself) to sublime morality.","Dan sesungguhnya engkau benar-benar berbudi pekerti yang luhur."],564,29,57,226,null,null],[5,5276,"68:5","فَسَتُبْصِرُ وَيُبْصِرُونَ",["So you shall see, and they (too) shall see,","Maka kelak engkau akan melihat dan mereka (orang-orang kafir) pun akan melihat,"],564,29,57,226,null,null],[6,5277,"68:6","بِأَييِّكُمُ الْمَفْتُونُ",["Which of you is afflicted with madness.","siapa di antara kamu yang gila?"],564,29,57,226,null,null],[7,5278,"68:7","إِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ أَعْلَمُ بِمَن ضَلَّ عَن سَبِيلِهِ وَهُوَ أَعْلَمُ بِالْمُهْتَدِينَ",["Surely your Lord best knows him who errs from His way, and He best knows the followers of the right course.","Sungguh, Tuhanmu, Dialah yang paling mengetahui siapa yang sesat dari jalan-Nya; dan Dialah yang paling mengetahui siapa orang yang mendapat petunjuk."],564,29,57,226,null,null],[8,5279,"68:8","فَلَا تُطِعِ الْمُكَذِّبِينَ",["So do not yield to the rejecters.","Maka janganlah engkau patuhi orang-orang yang mendustakan (ayat-ayat Allah)."],564,29,57,226,null,null],[9,5280,"68:9","وَدُّوا لَوْ تُدْهِنُ فَيُدْهِنُونَ",["They wish that you should be pliant so they (too) would be pliant.","Mereka menginginkan agar engkau bersikap lunak maka mereka bersikap lunak (pula)."],564,29,57,226,null,null],[10,5281,"68:10","وَلَا تُطِعْ كُلَّ حَلَّافٍ مَّهِينٍ",["And yield not to any mean swearer","Dan janganlah engkau patuhi setiap orang yang suka bersumpah dan suka menghina,"],564,29,57,226,null,null],[11,5282,"68:11","هَمَّازٍ مَّشَّاءٍ بِنَمِيمٍ",["Defamer, going about with slander","suka mencela, yang kian ke mari menyebarkan fitnah,"],564,29,57,226,null,null],[12,5283,"68:12","مَّنَّاعٍ لِّلْخَيْرِ مُعْتَدٍ أَثِيمٍ",["Forbidder of good, outstepping the limits, sinful,","yang merintangi segala yang baik, yang melampaui batas dan banyak dosa,"],564,29,57,226,null,null],[13,5284,"68:13","عُتُلٍّ بَعْدَ ذَٰلِكَ زَنِيمٍ",["Ignoble, besides all that, base-born;","yang bertabiat kasar, selain itu juga terkenal kejahatannya,"],564,29,57,226,null,null],[14,5285,"68:14","أَن كَانَ ذَا مَالٍ وَبَنِينَ",["Because he possesses wealth and sons.","karena dia kaya dan banyak anak."],564,29,57,226,null,null],[15,5286,"68:15","إِذَا تُتْلَىٰ عَلَيْهِ آيَاتُنَا قَالَ أَسَاطِيرُ الْأَوَّلِينَ",["When Our communications are recited to him, he says: Stories of those of yore.","Apabila ayat-ayat Kami dibacakan kepadanya, dia berkata, “(Ini adalah) dongeng-dongeng orang dahulu.”"],564,29,57,226,null,null],[16,5287,"68:16","سَنَسِمُهُ عَلَى الْخُرْطُومِ",["We will brand him on the nose.","Kelak dia akan Kami beri tanda pada belalai(nya)."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[17,5288,"68:17","إِنَّا بَلَوْنَاهُمْ كَمَا بَلَوْنَا أَصْحَابَ الْجَنَّةِ إِذْ أَقْسَمُوا لَيَصْرِمُنَّهَا مُصْبِحِينَ",["Surely We will try them as We tried the owners of the garden, when they swore that they would certainly cut off the produce in the morning,","Sungguh, Kami telah menguji mereka (orang musyrik Mekah) sebagaimana Kami telah menguji pemilik-pemilik kebun, ketika mereka bersumpah pasti akan memetik (hasil)nya pada pagi hari,"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[18,5289,"68:18","وَلَا يَسْتَثْنُونَ",["And were not willing to set aside a portion (for the poor).","tetapi mereka tidak menyisihkan (dengan mengucapkan, “Insya Allah”)."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[19,5290,"68:19","فَطَافَ عَلَيْهَا طَائِفٌ مِّن رَّبِّكَ وَهُمْ نَائِمُونَ",["Then there encompassed it a visitation from your Lord while they were sleeping.","Lalu kebun itu ditimpa bencana (yang datang) dari Tuhanmu ketika mereka sedang tidur."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[20,5291,"68:20","فَأَصْبَحَتْ كَالصَّرِيمِ",["So it became as black, barren land.","Maka jadilah kebun itu hitam seperti malam yang gelap gulita,"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[21,5292,"68:21","فَتَنَادَوْا مُصْبِحِينَ",["And they called out to each other in the morning,","lalu pada pagi hari mereka saling memanggil."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[22,5293,"68:22","أَنِ اغْدُوا عَلَىٰ حَرْثِكُمْ إِن كُنتُمْ صَارِمِينَ",["Saying: Go early to your tilth if you would cut (the produce).","”Pergilah pagi-pagi ke kebunmu jika kamu hendak memetik hasil.”"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[23,5294,"68:23","فَانطَلَقُوا وَهُمْ يَتَخَافَتُونَ",["So they went, while they consulted together secretly,","Maka mereka pun berangkat sambil berbisik-bisik."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[24,5295,"68:24","أَن لَّا يَدْخُلَنَّهَا الْيَوْمَ عَلَيْكُم مِّسْكِينٌ",["Saying: No poor man shall enter it today upon you.","”Pada hari ini jangan sampai ada orang miskin masuk ke dalam kebunmu.”"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[25,5296,"68:25","وَغَدَوْا عَلَىٰ حَرْدٍ قَادِرِينَ",["And in the morning they went, having the power to prevent.","Dan berangkatlah mereka pada pagi hari dengan niat menghalangi (orang-orang miskin) padahal mereka mampu (menolongnya)."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[26,5297,"68:26","فَلَمَّا رَأَوْهَا قَالُوا إِنَّا لَضَالُّونَ",["But when they saw it, they said: Most surely we have gone astray","Maka ketika mereka melihat kebun itu, mereka berkata, “Sungguh, kita ini benar-benar orang-orang yang sesat,"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[27,5298,"68:27","بَلْ نَحْنُ مَحْرُومُونَ",["Nay! we are made to suffer privation.","bahkan kita tidak memperoleh apa pun,”"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[28,5299,"68:28","قَالَ أَوْسَطُهُمْ أَلَمْ أَقُل لَّكُمْ لَوْلَا تُسَبِّحُونَ",["The best of them said: Did I not say to you, Why do you not glorify (Allah)?","berkatalah seorang yang paling bijak di antara mereka, “Bukankah aku telah mengatakan kepadamu, mengapa kamu tidak bertasbih (kepada Tuhanmu).”"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[29,5300,"68:29","قَالُوا سُبْحَانَ رَبِّنَا إِنَّا كُنَّا ظَالِمِينَ",["They said: Glory be to our Lord, surely we were unjust.","Mereka mengucapkan, “Mahasuci Tuhan kami, sungguh, kami adalah orang-orang yang zhalim.”"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[30,5301,"68:30","فَأَقْبَلَ بَعْضُهُمْ عَلَىٰ بَعْضٍ يَتَلَاوَمُونَ",["Then some of them advanced against others, blaming each other.","Lalu mereka saling berhadapan dan saling menyalahkan."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[31,5302,"68:31","قَالُوا يَا وَيْلَنَا إِنَّا كُنَّا طَاغِينَ",["Said they: O woe to us! surely we were inordinate:","Mereka berkata, “Celaka kita! Sesungguhnya kita orang-orang yang melampaui batas."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[32,5303,"68:32","عَسَىٰ رَبُّنَا أَن يُبْدِلَنَا خَيْرًا مِّنْهَا إِنَّا إِلَىٰ رَبِّنَا رَاغِبُونَ",["Maybe, our Lord will give us instead one better than it; surely to our Lord do we make our humble petition.","Mudah-mudahan Tuhan memberikan ganti kepada kita dengan (kebun) yang lebih baik daripada yang ini, sungguh, kita mengharapkan ampunan dari Tuhan kita.”"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[33,5304,"68:33","كَذَٰلِكَ الْعَذَابُ ۖ وَلَعَذَابُ الْآخِرَةِ أَكْبَرُ ۚ لَوْ كَانُوا يَعْلَمُونَ",["Such is the chastisement, and certainly the chastisement of the hereafter is greater, did they but know!","Seperti itulah azab (di dunia). Dan sungguh, azab akhirat lebih besar se-kiranya mereka mengetahui."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[34,5305,"68:34","إِنَّ لِلْمُتَّقِينَ عِندَ رَبِّهِمْ جَنَّاتِ النَّعِيمِ",["Surely those who guard (against evil) shall have with their Lord gardens of bliss.","Sungguh, bagi orang-orang yang bertakwa (disediakan) surga yang penuh kenikmatan di sisi Tuhannya."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[35,5306,"68:35","أَفَنَجْعَلُ الْمُسْلِمِينَ كَالْمُجْرِمِينَ",["What! shall We then make (that is, treat) those who submit as the guilty?","Apakah patut Kami memperlakukan orang-orang Islam itu seperti orang-orang yang berdosa (orang kafir)?"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[36,5307,"68:36","مَا لَكُمْ كَيْفَ تَحْكُمُونَ",["What has happened to you? How do you judge?","Mengapa kamu (berbuat demikian)? Bagaimana kamu mengambil keputusan?"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[37,5308,"68:37","أَمْ لَكُمْ كِتَابٌ فِيهِ تَدْرُسُونَ",["Or have you a book wherein you read,","Atau apakah kamu mempunyai kitab (yang diturunkan Allah) yang kamu pelajari?"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[38,5309,"68:38","إِنَّ لَكُمْ فِيهِ لَمَا تَخَيَّرُونَ",["That you have surely therein what you choose?","sesungguhnya kamu dapat memilih apa saja yang ada di dalamnya."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[39,5310,"68:39","أَمْ لَكُمْ أَيْمَانٌ عَلَيْنَا بَالِغَةٌ إِلَىٰ يَوْمِ الْقِيَامَةِ ۙ إِنَّ لَكُمْ لَمَا تَحْكُمُونَ",["Or have you received from Us an agreement confirmed by an oath extending to the day of resurrection that you shall surely have what you demand?","Atau apakah kamu memperoleh (janji-janji yang diperkuat dengan) sumpah dari Kami, yang tetap berlaku sampai hari Kiamat; bahwa kamu dapat mengambil keputusan (sekehendakmu)?"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[40,5311,"68:40","سَلْهُمْ أَيُّهُم بِذَٰلِكَ زَعِيمٌ",["Ask them which of them will vouch for that,","Tanyakanlah kepada mereka, “Siapakah di antara mereka yang bertanggung jawab terhadap (keputusan yang diambil itu)?”"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[41,5312,"68:41","أَمْ لَهُمْ شُرَكَاءُ فَلْيَأْتُوا بِشُرَكَائِهِمْ إِن كَانُوا صَادِقِينَ",["Or have they associates if they are truthful.","Atau apakah mereka mempunyai sekutu-sekutu? Kalau begitu hendaklah mereka mendatangkan sekutu-sekutunya jika mereka orang-orang yang benar."],565,29,57,226,null,null],[42,5313,"68:42","يَوْمَ يُكْشَفُ عَن سَاقٍ وَيُدْعَوْنَ إِلَى السُّجُودِ فَلَا يَسْتَطِيعُونَ",["On the day when there shall be a severe affliction, and they shall be called upon to make obeisance, but they shall not be able,","(Ingatlah) pada hari ketika betis disingkapkan dan mereka diseru untuk bersujud; maka mereka tidak mampu,"],565,29,57,226,null,null],[43,5314,"68:43","خَاشِعَةً أَبْصَارُهُمْ تَرْهَقُهُمْ ذِلَّةٌ ۖ وَقَدْ كَانُوا يُدْعَوْنَ إِلَى السُّجُودِ وَهُمْ سَالِمُونَ",["Their looks cast down, abasement shall overtake them; and they were called upon to make obeisance indeed while yet they were safe.","pandangan mereka tertunduk ke bawah, diliputi kehinaan. Dan sungguh, dahulu (di dunia) mereka telah diseru untuk bersujud pada waktu mereka sehat (tetapi mereka tidak melakukan)."],566,29,57,226,null,null],[44,5315,"68:44","فَذَرْنِي وَمَن يُكَذِّبُ بِهَٰذَا الْحَدِيثِ ۖ سَنَسْتَدْرِجُهُم مِّنْ حَيْثُ لَا يَعْلَمُونَ",["So leave Me and him who rejects this announcement; We will overtake them by degrees, from whence they perceive not:","Maka serahkanlah kepada-Ku (urusannya) dan orang-orang yang mendustakan perkataan ini (Al-Qur'an). Kelak akan Kami hukum mereka berangsur-angsur dari arah yang tidak mereka ketahui,"],566,29,57,226,null,null],[45,5316,"68:45","وَأُمْلِي لَهُمْ ۚ إِنَّ كَيْدِي مَتِينٌ",["And I do bear with them, surely My plan is firm.","dan Aku memberi tenggang waktu kepada mereka. Sungguh, rencana-Ku sangat teguh."],566,29,57,226,null,null],[46,5317,"68:46","أَمْ تَسْأَلُهُمْ أَجْرًا فَهُم مِّن مَّغْرَمٍ مُّثْقَلُونَ",["Or do you ask from them a reward, so that they are burdened with debt?","Ataukah engkau (Muhammad) meminta imbalan kepada mereka, sehingga mereka dibebani dengan hutang?"],566,29,57,226,null,null],[47,5318,"68:47","أَمْ عِندَهُمُ الْغَيْبُ فَهُمْ يَكْتُبُونَ",["Or have they (the knowledge of) the unseen, so that they write (it) down?","Ataukah mereka mengetahui yang gaib, lalu mereka menuliskannya?"],566,29,57,226,null,null],[48,5319,"68:48","فَاصْبِرْ لِحُكْمِ رَبِّكَ وَلَا تَكُن كَصَاحِبِ الْحُوتِ إِذْ نَادَىٰ وَهُوَ مَكْظُومٌ",["So wait patiently for the judgment of your Lord, and be not like the companion of the fish, when he cried while he was in distress.","Maka bersabarlah engkau (Muhammad) terhadap ketetapan Tuhanmu, dan janganlah engkau seperti (Yunus) orang yang berada dalam (perut) ikan ketika dia berdoa dengan hati sedih."],566,29,57,226,null,null],[49,5320,"68:49","لَّوْلَا أَن تَدَارَكَهُ نِعْمَةٌ مِّن رَّبِّهِ لَنُبِذَ بِالْعَرَاءِ وَهُوَ مَذْمُومٌ",["Were it not that favor from his Lord had overtaken him, he would certainly have been cast down upon the naked Found while he was blamed.","Sekiranya dia tidak segera mendapat nikmat dari Tuhannya, pastilah dia dicampakkan ke tanah tandus dalam keadaan tercela."],566,29,57,226,null,null],[50,5321,"68:50","فَاجْتَبَاهُ رَبُّهُ فَجَعَلَهُ مِنَ الصَّالِحِينَ",["Then his Lord chose him, and He made him of the good.","Lalu Tuhannya memilihnya dan menjadikannya termasuk orang yang shalih."],566,29,57,226,null,null],[51,5322,"68:51","وَإِن يَكَادُ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا لَيُزْلِقُونَكَ بِأَبْصَارِهِمْ لَمَّا سَمِعُوا الذِّكْرَ وَيَقُولُونَ إِنَّهُ لَمَجْنُونٌ",["And those who disbelieve would almost smite you with their eyes when they hear the reminder, and they say: Most surely he is mad.","Dan sungguh, orang-orang kafir itu hampir-hampir menggelincirkanmu dengan pandangan mata mereka, ketika mereka mendengar Al-Qur'an dan mereka berkata, “Dia (Muhammad) itu benar-benar orang gila.”"],566,29,57,226,null,null],[52,5323,"68:52","وَمَا هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكْرٌ لِّلْعَالَمِينَ",["And it is naught but a reminder to the nations.","Padahal (Al-Qur'an) itu tidak lain adalah peringatan bagi seluruh alam."],566,29,57,226,null,null]],[[[1,8,564,"&#xfb89;","word","ن",["Nun",""]],[2,8,564,"&#